Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I believe living in an on campus dorm during freshman year should be a requirement for college students. It is a great way to make new friends and get yourself out of your comfort zone by having to interact with people that you have not had the experience of interacting with in your life.